executionArgs.additionalInstruction: This is a Stellar/Soroban blockchain app running in DEV_MODE. Authentication uses auto-login via VITE_DEV_WALLET environment variable (wallet: GBZXN7PIRZGNMHGA7MUUUF4GWPY5AYPV6LY4UV2GL6VJGIQRXFDNMADI). The app auto-connects on page load. All blockchain operations return mock results in dev mode. Seed data includes: 5 invoices (draft, funding with contract_invoice_id=100, completed with contract_invoice_id=200, released with contract_invoice_id=300, cancelled), 4 businesses, 10 services, and multiple participants. The demo_user (user ID 1) is an admin with role='admin'. Invoice 2 (Cartagena Beach Trip) is in funding status and suitable for contribute/withdraw testing. The frontend runs on port 5173 and the backend API is at port 3000.
